{"type":"text","timestamp":1780729459643,"sessionID":"ses_164436567ffeteXLf4I1Mx29cA","part":{"id":"prt_e9bbf335b00136Wvv6R7HAYP4u","messageID":"msg_e9bbed8f00017iv2Bh2k6Bm4EF","sessionID":"ses_164436567ffeteXLf4I1Mx29cA","type":"text","text":"The cited MemClaw paths don’t support C2’s generated/manual causal-edge provenance claim. I’m doing one read-only pass over the named prior iteration artifacts only to avoid guessing the “prior verdict” column.","time":{"start":1780729459547,"end":1780729459639},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_093f04617cdaf9f7016a23c67389088191b75b574b1809f921","phase":"commentary"}}}}
